<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mere-adj">mere <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /mɪə(r)/    美 /mɪr/  </p>
<p>[只用于名词前，无比较级]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[强调小或微不足道] 仅仅的；只不过的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He lost the election by a mere 2 votes.
他只以两票之差落选。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[强调事物虽小但却有很大的影响] 极小的；极不重要的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The merest mention of snake makes her feel sick.
仅仅一提到蛇都会使她恶心。</p></div></div>